[SHORT DESC]
Gives 50% of exp earned in battle to one Pokemon.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>The Pokemon holding this item receives 50% of the experience points earned in battle, even if it has Klutz or is under the effect of Embargo. If more than one Pokemon is holding an Exp. Share, 50% of the experience points will be distributed equally amongst all Pokemon holding Exp. Shares.</p>